original_title: Peaches and Jesper Are On A Boat, Who Stays Afloat?
overview: Venice biennial, gondolas, unhappy couples, too much art. Peaches screaming an Italian opera to her sweet uninterested companion while strange poeple appear with black beards..who stays afloat?
